# About

The Wikimedia Developer Portal is a central entry point for Wikimedia technical documentation, created by the Wikimedia Foundation Developer Advocacy team.

This site is a prototype of the Developer Portal for content development and iteration. For more information about the project and to share your feedback, visit mediawiki.org (opens new window).
